reviewText: I loved Stranger With My Face it was very good and interesting and Alexz Johnson is a great actress and awesome

I have just started buying movies off amazon not that long ago and when I purchased this it was 2 days late which isn't a big deal just when I opened the packaging the case was broken. I don't wanna have to deal with sending it back for a new one but it would have been nice if the case wasn't broken on both sides.

Both films were very entertaining & held my interest. I particularly liked Stranger with my face. The second half of this movie became quite riveting. I found the use of astral projection as a major concept for the plot of this movie, to be a unique twist used by the writers of this film.
It was exactly what was advertised and I'm really glad I purchased it. I've been looking for this movie forever.  thanks alot great review!
